Preprocessing Data

shop.df <- setDF(shop)
set.seed(123)
train.index <- createDataPartition(shop.df$Revenue, p= .75,
                                   list= FALSE)
train.df <- shop.df[train.index, ]
valid.df <- shop.df[-train.index, ]

Logistic Regression

                  family = "binomial")
